Description.Text: An excellent hotel in the centre of Sharjah. RD05/08
The hotel is located on the edge of Sharjah's picturesque Khalid lagoon, fifteen minutes from both Sharjah and Dubai international airport.

The medium sized rooms are very well decorated with good quality dark wood furniture and contrasting bold coloured furnishings. Impeccable taste has been maintained throughout. The marble bathrooms are in excellent condition, as are the bedrooms.
This is a high-rise fourteen storey building in green and stone colour. There are lavish gardens to the front of the hotel with a wide driveway leading up to the majestic entrance way.
The hotel has several restaurants serving a variety of cuisines.

The large lobby is elegantly decorated in light marble with dark wood paneling. There is casual seating to the left of the lobby, whilst the main buffet restaurant is to the back of the lobby, with the new authentic seafood restaurant to the right.
